vg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uld1665702653667.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uld1665702653667.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uld1665702653667.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uld1665702653667\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /con (and /anm)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Analyze modeled entities and create entity descriptors for entities that share the same model name.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uld1665702653667__section_w2138ab1b5b1_w2139ab1b5_w2140ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uld1665702653667__p_d148247e1_d148248e1_d148249e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/con</span> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inf</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/war</span>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/tpl</span>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/plt</span>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Datetime</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Datetime</var>} { {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uld1665702653667__section_w2141ab1b5b3_w2142ab1b5_w2143ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d303470e98\">\n                  \n Switches\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uld1665702653667__li_d51488e1_d51489e1_d51490e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"czj1665702653450.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/czj1665702653450.html\" title=\"Display the information listing plus warning and error messages when compiling.\">/inf</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uld1665702653667__li_d51491e1_d51492e1_d51493e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wmw1665702653597.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wmw1665702653597.html\" title=\"Display warning and error messages when compiling.\">/war</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uld1665702653667__li_d51494e1_d51495e1_d51496e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fmo1665702653737.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fmo1665702653737.html\" title=\"Compiles main development objects that are defined as templates (Purpose = T), but does not generate runtime objects. Use it to ensure that templates do not contain ProcScript syntax errors.\">/tpl</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uld1665702653667__li_d51497e1_d51498e1_d51499e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"twc1665702654010.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/twc1665702654010.html\" title=\"Compiles main development objects that are defined as palettes (Purpose = P), but does not generate runtime objects. Use it to ensure that palettes do not contain ProcScript syntax errors.\">/plt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uld1665702653667__li_d51500e1_d51501e1_d51502e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ide1665702625805.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ide1665702625805.html\" title=\"Compile objects modified after and/or before the date specified.\">/aft= or /bef=</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uld1665702653667__section_w2144ab1b5b5_w2145ab1b5_w2146ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d303470e169\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uld1665702653667__d6306e22\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>—name of an entity in the specified model. If specified, <var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var> must also be specified.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uld1665702653667__d6306e31\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>—model name or search profile to use as selector for the modeled entities to analyze; if omitted, all application models are analyzed.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uld1665702653667__section_w2147ab1b5b7_w2148ab1b5_w2149ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d303470e193\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uld1665702653667__d5931e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.exe</span>—Uniface IDE</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uld1665702653667__section_w2150ab1b5b9_w2151ab1b5_w2152ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d303470e205\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uld1665702653667__p_d148265e1_d148266e1_d148267e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inf</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/war</span> sub-switches to increase the amount of information displayed when analyzing.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uld1665702653667__p_d148268e1_d148269e1_d148270e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/tpl</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/plt</span> sub-switches if you want to compile modeled entities that are defined as templates or palettes. By default, these are not compiled by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/con</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uld1665702653667__section_w2153ab1b5c11_w2154ab1b5_w2155ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d303470e233\">Example: Compiling Modeled Entities </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Compile all entities in the model</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/con model</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Compile an entity in a specific model</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/con entity.model</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Compile an entity in specified models</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/con entity.mo*</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Compile a specified entity in any model</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uld1665702653667__p_d148274e1_d148275e1_d148276e1\">The model must be specified, in this case as a wildcard:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/con entity.*</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532731\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532731\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/con (and /anm) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /con (and /anm) Analyze modeled entities and create entity descriptors for entities that share the same model name. /con { /inf | /war } { /tpl } { /plt } { /aft= Datetime } { /bef = Datetime } { { Entity . } Model } Switches /inf /war /tpl /plt /aft= or /bef= Parameters Entity —name of an entity in the specified model. If specified, Model must also be specified. Model —model name or search profile to use as selector for the modeled entities to analyze; if omitted, all application models are analyzed. Use With ide.exe —Uniface IDE Description Use the /inf and /war sub-switches to increase the amount of information displayed when analyzing. Use the /tpl and /plt sub-switches if you want to compile modeled entities that are defined as templates or palettes. By default, these are not compiled by /con . Example: Compiling Modeled Entities Compile all entities in the model /con model Copy Compile an entity in a specific model /con entity.model Copy Compile an entity in specified models /con entity.mo* Copy Compile a specified entity in any model The model must be specified, in this case as a wildcard: /con entity.* Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}